 Castile, wife of  Edward I ."]},{"name":"Elinor","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Eleanor ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Eleanor de Norris was born in 1140, in England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Robert de Turberville. She died in 1168, at the age of 28."},"et":{"1140–1168":"1140–1168","1140–1182":"1140–1182","1155–1215":"1155–1215","1215":"1215","ABT 1155":"umbes 1155","1168":"1168","1155":"1155","1140":"1140","1182":"1182","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Salford, Oxfordshire":"Salford, Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1140–1168":"1140–1168","1140–1182":"1140–1182","1155–1215":"1155–1215","1215":"1215","ABT 1155":"noin 1155","1168":"1168","1155":"1155","1140":"1140","1182":"1182","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Salford, Oxfordshire":"Salford, Oxfordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1140–1168":"1140–1168","1140–1182":"1140–1182","1155–1215":"1155–1215","1215":"1215","ABT 1155":"environ 1155","1168":"1168","1155":"1155","1140":"1140","1182":"1182","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Salford, Oxfordshire":"Salford, Oxfordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Eleanor de Norris est née en 1140, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Robert de Turberville. Elle est décédée en 1168, à l’âge de 28 ans."},"de":{"1140–1168":"1140–1168","1140–1182":"1140–1182","1155–1215":"1155–1215","1215":"1215","ABT 1155":"um 1155","1168":"1168","1155":"1155","1140":"1140","1182":"1182","England":"England, United Kingdom","Salford, Oxfordshire":"Salford, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Eleanor de Norris wurde 1140 in England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit Robert de Turberville mindestens 1 Tochter. Sie starb 1168 im Alter von 28 Jahren."},"ht":{"1140–1168":"1140–1168","1140–1182":"1140–1182","1155–1215":"1155–1215","1215":"1215","ABT 1155":"about 1155","1168":"1168","1155":"1155","1140":"1140","1182":"1182","England":"Angletè, United Kingdom","Salford, Oxfordsh